        self.labels = y
        
        logits = np.exp(self.logits)
        logits_sum = np.sum(logits, axis=1)
        self.sm = logits / logits_sum[:, None]
        loss = -np.sum(y * np.log(self.sm), axis=1)
        
        return loss
